{"tid":1352224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對準政權 同 光復元朗其實係冇衝突！","createTime":"2019-07-22T17:59:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T12:53:35.000Z","uid":91967,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"63980f8c74d4e130295d1bf80aff477ffc4d0452","tid":1352224,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:59:34.000Z","msg":"光復元朗其實對我地好有好處<br />\n<br />\n<strong>民意方面：</strong><br />\n經過721既元朗恐襲，我諗大部份嘅香港人都會對班鄉黑同黑警既不作為感到好憤怒。光復元朗可以令更多人企喺我地呢邊，我地係<span style=\"color: red;\">為民請命</span>。<br />\n<br />\n同時，令更多香港人贊同<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武抗爭，以武制暴</span>既理念。<br />\n<br />\n另外，我地既其中一個<span style=\"color: red;\">目標係黑警</span>，打破警察制度既唔公義。唔通元朗恐襲入面既警黑勾結唔係源自制度既唔公義？講唔去。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>對抗爭運動既好處：</strong><br />\n721中環事件，黑警開咗30幾槍都冇引起關注，好大程度係因為元朗恐襲<span style=\"color: red;\">吸走注意</span>，包括連登仔。<br />\n<br />\n吸走咗注意力，<span style=\"color: red;\">對我哋嘅義士黎講係非常危險</span>，就算佢地面對既情況有幾危險，我哋都未必提供到幫助。同時，616二百萬人遊行都係因為大家睇到612示威者既慘況而激發出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n如果我地下次再有大型行動，政府又<span style=\"color: red;\">派多次黑社會打人</span>，我地既義士又會少咗人理，對佢地好危險。<br />\n<br />\n同時，會<span style=\"color: red;\">污名化示威運動</span>，有香港人會將示威同黑社會打人關連，覺得我地示威就會黑社會出黎打人。<br />\n<br />\n總而言之，光復元朗係<span style=\"color: red;\">非常迫切</span>。因為我地唔搞掂呢單，只會有更多更多單。"},{"pid":"94a9920f44dd0135e9abef116ad28054fbb04d73","tid":1352224,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:59:46.000Z","msg":"大家幫推"},{"pid":"eeb1ef1e59de586ba8300c76ffa0572e44d6f7e6","tid":1352224,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:08:56.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"658b19fbaaa75263d011e1956084570a247c22fd","tid":1352224,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:09:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a50d560262507301f26c24a75466c737a6a33309","tid":1352224,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:12:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd9ac778d431e80c942177eb3785a2f1619688c7","tid":1352224,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:13:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cebd9920c8dc6e036dd2cf8949b3290c24e2b193","tid":1352224,"uid":281418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:14:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fac1bbe23d0d8c37d18bb87944efa6b1449aa328","tid":1352224,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:15:12.000Z","msg":"不服來辯"},{"pid":"7dda99c1ce1980d492977f29278e3d529cae7ca7","tid":1352224,"uid":174953,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:16:23.000Z","msg":"又有三毛開始帶風向，分化727光復元朗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1352213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1352213</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5166de693d31a1dfe8f63a30195f6dd0353c29a6","tid":1352224,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dda99c1ce1980d492977f29278e3d529cae7ca7","tid":1352224,"uid":174953,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:16:23.000Z","msg":"又有三毛開始帶風向，分化727光復元朗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1352213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1352213</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:16:59.000Z","msg":"巴打同我所見略同"},{"pid":"a45b2435e2a6b49b081ab606597124ab9cfb5763","tid":1352224,"uid":59989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3f247d50d83191c4a658478727e122e4ceb811","tid":1352224,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:18:54.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"bf343c0efae5412a2730b70e854214b952c2c600","tid":1352224,"uid":280625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:19:11.000Z","msg":"認同推"},{"pid":"d90eed0295977adf085eba3fbc6eb2be54798ca8","tid":1352224,"uid":2908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:19:43.000Z","msg":"